thread.title: Station : lovehatehimのblog
thread.title_full: Station : lovehatehimのblog

posts.title: Station : lovehatehimのblog
posts.text: Station I live just next to a station. At early morning, people are few, but after a few while people fully fill the station, and only this while the station gets to be a big city. But after that at any time zone, people at the station gets to be sparse. At evening time people’s number gets to increase, many people get off and on the train again. After that people’s number decreases near the last train arrival and departure, a little bit more people’s number increases and after the last train, the station gets to be tacit again. After sending last train, the station’s shutters lift down, some people hasten to other side of the railroad in the station concourse. But they’re very rare. People who stays at the station is none but the station attendants. Station is usually the space where anyone just passes over. There’s a station without anytime infrequent people use all day long. From the station next to my residence you can arrive at that station in 20minutes and a little. In big city, almost all of station are fully filled with so countless people. But very few station is different. It is city’s interesting content. But there’s a station only infrequent people rarely use those platforms. But its fact gets to be known to anybody in this country and so many people from to and fro in this country come there and take photographs. I also want to go there before they get to be known to anybody. People often say that people should not alter a way to live. But possibly it would not be wrong to alter a way to live often. Because its action is the evidence which any actor of life doesn’t abandon their ideal. Station probably know all of people’s things as getting off and on. Then also stations cry for narrowness of space their platforms hold, you might reform them. Dawn time station, morning glow time station, all day long cloudy desolate station, midsummer hotness burning rooftops of platforms and station building, Downpour rainy station. Snow covered station. Station knows all of reason’s all of changes and everything happens there. If you have not known something, you might visit to the station and observe any seasons and anytime aspect quietly not using the train to get off or on. You can discover something with it. If you can’t abandon something, you might go to the station and listen to station’s voice. Station people say farewell to each other, station people meet at the first time, station people see each other after a long not meeting time. Only station knows all of those. Thereby the station would sustain you. (6 th Oct. revised at 11 th Oct.) カテゴリなしの他の記事

投稿日 2017年10月15日 08:51:36 （IT・科学） スポンサーリンク 1 A businessman has given a warning proving why you should never put anything down on an escalator. 
Philipp Bellessort placed his laptop case by his feet, with his £1,000 MacBook Pro inside. 
The 28-year-old then heard a crunching noise and realised the bag had been sucked into the escalator steps as they rose, completely chewing up his laptop . 
His new computer was completely ruined by the London Tube escalator, leaving it curled up like a piece of paper. 
The freak accident tore the bag but also crushed the laptop, twisting the metal and completely destroying the device ? including three months of hard work that it contained.
